{{Vgname|杀出重围|en=Deus Ex|cn=杀出重围|tw=駭客入侵}}<ref name="Nuwen1">{{cite web |url=http://nuwen.net/dx.html |title=Deus Ex - nuwen.net |accessdate=2007-12-13 |language=en |archive-date=2012-01-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64z1SsXFX?url=http://nuwen.net/dx.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一款[[动作角色扮演游戏|动作角色扮演游戏]]，由[[离子风暴|离子风暴]]公司开发、[[Eidos_Interactive|Eidos Interactive]]于2000年发行，结合了第一人称射击和角色扮演的元素。该游戏广受好评，获选为[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]评出的电脑游戏百强第一名<ref name='PCGTop100'>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamertop100.com/editorial/10-1 |title=PCGamer Top 100 |accessdate=2009-12-16 |date=2009-12-16 |work=PC Gamer |publisher=Future Publishing |language=en |archive-date=2010-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210203935/http://www.pcgamertop100.com/editorial/10-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及英国游戏杂志《[[PC_Zone|PC Zone]]》读者投票选出的“有史以来最佳电脑游戏”。<ref name="gamesindustry">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/deus-ex-named-top-pc-game-of-all-time |title=Deus Ex named "top PC game of all time (pc: 2007):Reviews |work=gamesindustry |accessdate=September 7, 2007 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817182418/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/deus-ex-named-top-pc-game-of-all-time |dead-url=no }}</ref>它经常被选入[[年度游戏|年度游戏]]奖，<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/pc/deusex?q=Deus%20Ex |title=Deus Ex (pc: 2000):Reviews |work=Metacritic |accessdate=December 13, 2006 |language=en |archive-date=2009-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225193839/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/pc/deusex?q=deus%20ex |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mobygames">{{cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/windows/deus-ex |title=Deus Ex for Windows |work=MobyGames |accessdate=December 13, 2006 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117133435/https://www.mobygames.com/game/windows/deus-ex |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Bafta">{{cite web |url=http://videogames.yahoo.com/newsarticle?eid=357210&page=0 |title=Deus Ex Receives British Award |publisher=Yahoo! |work=Yahoo! Games |author=Trey Walker |accessdate=2006-07-24 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070314024451/http://videogames.yahoo.com/newsarticle?eid=357210&page=0 |archivedate=2007-03-14 }}</ref><ref name="GDC">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamechoiceawards.com/archive/gdca_1st.htm |title=Archive/1st Annual Game Developers Choice Awards |work=Game Developers Choice Awards |accessdate=December 15, 2006 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061016193916/http://www.gamechoiceawards.com/archive/gdca_1st.htm |archivedate=2006年10月16日 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>其玩家选择和多重叙事路径方面的先锋性设计赢得了评论家的赞赏。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://doublebuffered.com/2008/10/20/why-deus-ex-is-important/ |title=Why Deus Ex Is Important |work=Double Buffered |accessdate=March 15, 2009 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313064618/http://doublebuffered.com/2008/10/20/why-deus-ex-is-important/ |archivedate=2009年3月13日 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2008/06/06/remembering-deus-ex/ |title=Remembering 'Deus Ex' — One Of Modern Gaming's First Titles Offering Real Player Choice |work=[[MTV|MTV]] |accessdate=March 15, 2009 |language=en |archive-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919225913/http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2008/06/06/remembering-deus-ex/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2009年4月23日，该游戏被卖出超过100万份。<ref name="ve3d">{{cite web|url=http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/46400/Eidos-Square-Enix-Sales-Figures-Revealed|first=Andrew|last=Burnes|title=Eidos & Square Enix Sales Figures Revealed|work=Voodoo Extreme|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=April 23, 2009|accessdate=September 7, 2011|language=en|archive-date=2009-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427222317/http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/46400/Eidos-Square-Enix-Sales-Figures-Revealed|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2003年推出續集《[[駭客入侵：隱形戰爭|駭客入侵：隱形戰爭]]》，以及2011年的前傳《[[駭客入侵：人類革命|駭客入侵：人類革命]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16365 |title = Eidos Announces Deus Ex 3, Talks New Montreal Studio |author = Leigh Alexander |date = 2007-11-26 |publisher = Gamasutra |language = en |access-date = 2016-02-12 |archive-date = 2016-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502180328/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=16365 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2015年，發行商[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]]宣佈前傳續集《[[駭客入侵：人類分裂|駭客入侵：人類分裂]]》，於2016年8月23日推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/games/1404274/deus-ex-mankind-divided-release-date-videos-pre-order |title = Deus Ex: Mankind Divided - release date, videos & pre-order |author = Seth Barton |date = 2016-01-12 |publisher = Expert Reviews |language = en |access-date = 2016-02-12 |archive-date = 2016-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160216230416/http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/games/1404274/deus-ex-mankind-divided-release-date-videos-pre-order |dead-url = no }}</ref>

游戏设定在2052年的[[反乌托邦|反乌托邦]]世界，主角是新进的联合国反恐联盟特工JC·丹顿，他要在混乱的世界中与恐怖分子势力作斗争。随着剧情的展开，丹顿陷入了一场久远而深重的阴谋，在他的旅途中遇到了Majestic 12、[[光明會|光明會]]、香港[[黑社会|黑社会]]等形形色色的组织。

